,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"3c2bc307c65e18e0866756983a145922b628e9bf","tid":2048042,"uid":180168,"like":62,"dislike":3,"score":59,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T14:07:07.000Z","msg":"律政司隨時上訴<br />\n我覺得都係避免接受訪問好啲<br />\n可能佢以為入硬"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T14:10:48.000Z","msg":"你識唔識法律？<br />\n要有關鍵性新證據律政司先有得上訴"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T14:19:50.000Z","msg":"律政司不服裁決上訴經常都有<br />\n總之個人認為暫時判咗無罪就低調啲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T15:10:51.000Z","msg":"佢無咩講事發經過應該無事既"},{"pid":"7ae11b0015132c8aec7bba0aefabb20ec68b6d7c","tid":2048042,"uid":172172,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6235d2c46d566319b919d9ae614636e234aa696a","tid":2048042,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T13:50:07.000Z","msg":"「案件押後明天裁決！」法官昨日（6 月 1 日）一個決定，令被告欄內、被控暴動罪的林同學愕然不已。<br />\n<br />\n林同學原以為，法官至少會相隔一周才作出裁決，故即使「最壞打算」遭裁定罪成，仍有時間與親友逐一道別，「但想不到咁快裁決&hellip;&hellip;心情好似坐過山車咁。」不足 24 小時後，或許就要失去數年的自由，心情難免複雜。<br />\n<br />\n裁決前數小時，林同學接受《立場新聞》專訪，沒流露太多情緒。「後悔就無，擔心就有，因為完全掌握唔到，不知會發生咩事。」<br />\n<br />\n詳細訪問：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%B0%88%E8%A8%AA-%E9%A6%96%E5%AE%97%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95%E7%BD%AA%E5%90%8D%E4%B8%8D%E6%88%90%E7%AB%8B-20-%E6%AD%B2%E6%9E%97%E5%90%8C%E5%AD%B8%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E5%BA%A6%E9%81%8E%E8%A3%81%E6%B1%BA%E5%89%8D%E6%9C%80%E5%BE%8C-24-%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25B0%2588%25E8%25A8%25AA-%25E9%25A6%2596%25E5%25AE%2597%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E5%2590%258D%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2588%2590%25E7%25AB%258B-20-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E6%259E%2597%25E5%2590%258C%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E5%25A6%2582%25E4%25BD%2595%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E9%2581%258E%25E8%25A3%2581%25E6%25B1%25BA%25E5%2589%258D%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25BE%258C-24-%25E5%25B0%258F%25E6%2599%2582%2F&d=9MYRmPDtC2YjWedq%2F%2FxxgceYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=def97c53\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.th